19-6-0-use-serve-static-preview-for-comm.description: Use serve-static or preview for webServerCommand.

update-19-6-0-add-e2e-ci-target-defaults.description: Add inferred ciTargetNames to targetDefaults with dependsOn to ensure dependent application builds are scheduled before atomized tasks.

update-21-3-0-notify-about-merging-atomi.description: Logs a message to inform users of the new feature that merges atomized tasks reports by default in the 'e2e-ci' target. It provides information on how to opt-out of this behavior. It doesn't perform any changes to the workspace.
